name: Animated Dreams
description:
Animated Dreams

A multipurpose ANIMATION style (not just anime) model. This doesn't produce animated items, you need an application on apple/android OR an A1111 Extension called Deforum.

TEST SPACE ON HUGGINGFACE:

https://huggingface.co/spaces/Duskfallcrew/Animated_Dreams

What's in the training data and why is it a little different than most:

  1. I trained it on "DIGITAL VIVID MEMORIES" for about 3500 steps

  2. Data has not just Genshin, Anime but some nijijourney data and some cough MEITU OUTPUT RUNS! *

  3. This model WILL BITE YOU in the night and make you breakfast in the morning while stealing not just your car but your husband kids and everyone else in the neighborhood.

Coffee is nice:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

Concept tag: Meitu

  • Please note lmao, we are NOT at fault for any ToS of that app (MEITU) and we are NOT at fault for anyone on tumblr crying at you for using our model.

  • Also safe tensors WILL COME SOON, i'm at a backlog for these.

  • SAFE TENSORS JUST ADDED!

  • MOre images to come, the uploader cried at the GIF LMAO.

Creative Open-M Lisc: https://huggingface.co/spaces/CompVis/stable-diffusion-license

Only thing we ask is if you commericalize this model that you do deposit sugar daddy level money at our Ko_Fi, cause holy crap if you're gonna charge moola to use our stuff - give us a 5 or 10 lol.
